rows.label: qst400206_msg0001
rows.name:
Sorry... I'm only interested
in plants, so I'm not really
up on the latest rumors.

rows.label: qst400206_msg0002
rows.name:
I want to be a botanist in Superbia,
but my parents are against it.
They say it's too dangerous.

rows.label: qst400206_msg0003
rows.name:
It's been ten years since the
truce between the Superbian Empire
and the Invidian Dominion...

rows.label: qst400206_msg0004
rows.name:
And I know that shady group Iira has
been popping up recently, but...

rows.label: qst400206_msg0005
rows.name:
Nothing bad could happen under
the Empire's rule. This peaceful
town is proof! Right?
